# Bucket A — local-only Claude config, instructions and hooks.
# The repo root IS the live site, so these must never be committed/published.
# They load from disk regardless of git status; this file keeps them off
# pedaldiary.iamcoding.uk. (Bucket-B pages such as buddy.html are NOT listed
# here — they are meant to be committed and served, just unlisted.)
.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# OS cruft — can leak local file/directory listings if committed.
.DS_Store

# Editor workspace settings — harmless but fetchable if committed.
.vscode/
